{FARMING }
There are no large,intensive farms in this area.Many of the farms are small holdings.The main type of farming is in fact dairying with crops being grown to be used on the farms not as a profit making concern.
{FORESTRY}
A large proportion of our block is covered with forestry.The forested area is land which has been drained and reclaimed from the moss.It has been planted out with quick growing conifers.However a few patches of deciduous trees can be found.The areas of woodland are privately owned and have no connection with the Forestry Commission.
